ToDo List for Nhopkg (the way to Nhopkg 0.6)
============================================

If you want to contribute with Nhopkg development, send me a mail (projectnhoax@gmail.com).

	* Search package dependencies in configure.ac script or similar file (auto-package option).
	* Less time to create binary package.
	* Add support to use local (/home/user/.nhopkg/nhopkg.conf) configuration file.
	* Progress bar for downloads (without using wget progress bar).
	* Option to add conflicts packages.
	* Search orphan, obsolete and newest packages.
	* rpm2nho
	* deb2nho
	* PKGBUILD2nhoid (for archlinux packages)
	* ...
	* A lot of things.